At FC Famalicao, Vaz Pinto had a dismal performance wining only four matches out of the 26 he oversaw at the club.The tactician also served for only seven days at Ghanaian giants Heart of Oak after disagreeing with the management over the realignment of the technical bench. Gor Mahia's new coach, Carlos Manuel Vaz Pinto, says his main target is to help the club qualify for the Caf Confederation Cup group stages in February. 

Portuguese Vaz Pinto was unveiled on Sunday on a two-year contract and is tasked with changing the club's fortunes in the Confederation Cup. 

Gor exited the lucrative Caf Champions League in the first round after an 8-1 aggregate loss to CR Belouizdad of Algeria last week. 



